  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Agro-hydro meteorological services Advancement in Ethiopia (CMESA-E)</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The project aims to establish improved meteorological information provision in Ethiopia. It aims to develop a comprehensive national framework on climate services; to improve the knowledge and evidence base for agro-hydro meteorological services; and to establish and foster stakeholder learning and dialogue platforms on climate services.</narrative>
